### Create a deck
POST http://localhost:4000/api/decks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "My Awesome Deck",
  "description": "Test deck",
  "cards": ["Card1", "Card2", "Card3", "Card4", "Card5", "Card6", "Card7", "Card8"],
  "isPublic": true
}

### Get all decks
GET http://localhost:4000/api/decks

### Get deck by ID
GET http://localhost:4000/api/decks/1

### Update deck
PUT http://localhost:4000/api/decks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Deck Name"
}

### Delete deck
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/decks/1

### Like a deck
POST http://localhost:4000/api/decks/1/like

### Get stats
GET http://localhost:4000/api/decks/stats

### Health check
GET http://localhost:4000/health